description: This Chainlink VRF top 10% score Gatinho purrs with a rating of 53, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 159, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, Nine Lives for East, 1 for South, and 3 for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/50533-69132-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [159 Votes, Top 10% Score]
